Item
	

Description

MSTID
	

MSTP instance ID.

Port
	

-

Role
	
Interface role:

    DESI: Designated port

    ROOT: Root port

    ALTE: Alternate port

    BACK: Backup port

    MAST: Master port

    DISA: The interface is in initialization state.

STP State
	
Interface status. In the CIST region, the statuses of interfaces are as follows:

    FORWARDING

    LEARNING

    DISCARDING

Protection
	
Protection function:

    ROOTPROTECTION
    LOOPPROTECTION
    NONE
